13T05:44:51.000Z","msg":"最重要係安全<br />\n每個都要平安,同埋有咩事真係要退,唔好死留"},{"pid":"b2364b682b81c9e59044fbb81d529a4dd890f6e7","tid":1650553,"uid":223260,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5f78eaa0e1a7ef1e80e8fd81f85cbb2087bbb9f9","tid":1650553,"uid":254923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T04:32:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/10/13/122705_2740d6af4e84b5973fb5e5a03e8cc02f.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F10%2F13%2F122705_2740d6af4e84b5973fb5e5a03e8cc02f.gif&h=d15fd1e1&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/10/13/122724_540b55eef47fafaeaa6a3f78dbf36554.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F10%2F13%2F122724_540b55eef47fafaeaa6a3f78dbf36554.gif&h=d273dcd1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GJ1QB5G.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGJ1QB5G.gif&h=74c77e57&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ohxXg5L.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FohxXg5L.gif&h=7b418121&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TjLFeSt.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTjLFeSt.gif&h=69f8c95e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2gpKGxw.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2gpKGxw.gif&h=45ff934d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0JaBxEE.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0JaBxEE.gif&h=3d5d494d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fOBdzTa.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfOBdzTa.gif&h=3c4fdc4a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XwifOde.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXwifOde.gif&h=1416b25f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我會話比你聽係<span style=\"color: red;\">勇氣</span><br />\n呢樣嘢可以決定一切<br />\n<br />\n出發前問下自己可以去到幾盡，調整好心態，保持平常心。<br />\n我哋今日見"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T05:47:01.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/sHe1nvuuzRE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FsHe1nvuuzRE&d=BELmNDq%2B1pqro4agOzjMGb7WCVQ3d6ncBxZnFa%2FO6Ec%3D&h=aa71cebb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/sHe1nvuuzRE</a> <br />\n<br />\n驀然回望 過去吋土頃刻赤荒 失去願望<br />\r\n定然無望 也要勇敢穿起武裝 懷著滿目曙光 <br />\r\n忘記現狀 仍回眸失意怎麼茁壯 <br />\r\n前事儘管淡忘 明日再起床便拒絕怯慌 <br />\r\n<br />\r\n伴我走 在漆黑之中同行 <br />\r\n別放手 縱使得不到答允<br />\r\n無論再艱苦都抱緊一顆赤心<br />\r\n<br />\r\n未怕傷 目光中不管旁人<br />\r\n讓理想 再一點點的靠近 <br />\r\n重新修補缺陷 倘深深不忿 <br />\r\n總可一再集訓 跌過再翻身 <br />\r\n<br />\r\n突然沿岸 佈滿暗湧怎麼格檔 千尺巨浪 <br />\r\n地搖岩蕩 也要奮身穿街過巷 平地會在遠方 <br />\r\n橫過直撞 才能尋找最佳的拍檔 <br />\r\n尋夢未可獨航 如士氣高昂便繼續拓荒<br />\r\n<br />\r\n伴我走 在漆黑之中同行 別放手 縱使得不到答允 <br />\r\n無論再艱苦都抱緊一顆赤心 未怕傷 目光中不管旁人 <br />\r\n讓理想 再一點點的靠近 重新修補缺陷 倘深深不忿 <br />\r\n總可一再集訓 跌過再翻身 <br />\r\n<br />\r\n要再等 任多麽心急如焚 <br />\r\n亦強忍 任多少損失氣憤 <br />\r\n前路再崎嶇不要緊不准變更 <br />\r\n要記緊 路可找到於明晨 <br />\r\n用信心 成功都只因發奮 昂首方可上陣<br />\r\n輸了亦無謂淚滲 來汲取教訓"},{"pid":"34fe5327760c00a2c924351e362dca8b7f644eaf","tid":1650553,"uid":95390,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T05:47:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/usEKGYD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FusEKGYD.jpg&h=6ea50012&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n記住我地既手足"},{"pid":"ed2e932e90cbdd16ed8be24e16aadf1e4de92c3a","tid":1650553,"uid":184366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T05:48:09.000Z","msg":"推啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98ce6a56127d0b9304c68bb37b914dc15cc4863e","tid":1650553,"uid":295053,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T05:48:28.000Z","msg":"